      • findMatchingEntry

        public static final LocalForwardingEntry findMatchingEntry(String host,
                                                           int port,
                                                           Collection<? extends LocalForwardingEntry> entries)
        Parameters:
        host - The host - ignored if null/empty - i.e., no match reported
        port - The port - ignored if non-positive - i.e., no match reported
        entries - The Collection of LocalForwardingEntry to check - ignored if null/empty - i.e., no match reported
        Returns:
        The first entry whose host or alias matches the host name - case sensitive and has a matching port - null if no match found
